B.Jr=new A.bg(B.bq,["ADS (INSTAGRAM, TV, YOUTUBE)",'Whether you are targeting a local niche or a global audience, our Commercial & Ad Production service focuses on high-conversion storytelling. We create visually arresting content tailored for the specific technical requirements of Instagram, TV, and YouTube, ensuring your brand message is optimized for both the small screen and the living room. From 15-second "scroll-stopping" social clips to high-production broadcast spots, we help you turn viewers into customers through cinematic precision and strategic messaging.',0],t.l)
B.Jq=new A.bg(B.bq,["PRODUCT PROMOS","Our Product Promo Video service is designed to make your merchandise the hero of its own story. Move beyond flat photos and show your customers exactly how your product looks, moves, and solves their problems with engaging, kinetic visuals. We blend high-end cinematography\u2014focusing on textures, functionality, and aesthetic detail\u2014with strategic marketing to create promos that don't just display a product, but create an urge to own it.",200],t.l)
B.Jw=new A.bg(B.bq,["SALES-DRIVEN CONTENT",'Our Sales-Driven Content service is engineered for one specific purpose: conversion. We move beyond general awareness to create high-impact visuals that address customer pain points, overcome objections, and provide a clear, persuasive call to action. By combining psychological triggers with high-quality production, we develop assets that sit at the bottom of your marketing funnel\u2014designed to turn "interest" into "revenue."',400],t.l)
